      "name": "Image Source Field",
      "summary": "The Image Source definition manages different methods of specifying images within cards, supporting either direct URL input or uploaded file linkage. It provides fields for inputting an image URL, linking to an uploaded image file, and selecting the source mode between URL and file. The definition includes logic to resolve the active image URL based on the selected mode, facilitating dynamic and flexible image rendering within card components. It offers embedded and edit templates for displaying and modifying the image source in user interfaces.",
